@* THE BOUNDARY of decision 145: a DateTime is its BigInt tick count (decision 115), and a tick count
   has no Kind -- DateTimeKind does not survive the erasure. Valid Blazor (an enum renders fine there);
   deliberately refused here, with wording that names the erasure. *@

<p><span id="out">@stamp.Kind</span></p>

<button id="go" @onclick="Go">go</button>

@code {
    private System.DateTime stamp;

    private void Go()
    {
        stamp = System.DateTime.UtcNow;
    }
}
